{"tid":273401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【但有一個夢】南炮第一大Bang TOP疑自殺","createTime":"2017-06-06T13:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T13:58:08.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4de537c98b69004252aee8bc428b3eae9f47201","tid":273401,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"最近BIGBANG成員T.O.P被爆去年10月曾跟女練習生韓瑞希同屋吸食大麻，遭檢察院予以不拘留起訴，等待審判，形象插水。今日（6日）他就被發現暈倒在家，失去意識，被送往深切治療部，據悉他有服藥過多的可能性。而月前入伍的他原本隸屬首爾地方員警廳，昨日（5日）因醜聞被調職到首爾陽川區新月洞第4機動隊，是事件公開後首度現身，他手執行李、面帶微笑地急步離開警廳，但未有開腔回應記者提問。而今天首爾警察廳就表示，判定T.O.P並不適合，為警隊宣傳，擔任樂隊義務警察，所以將其調動到第4機動隊，而昨日調職後T.O.P在勤務地點也一直處於待命狀態，未有被賦予職務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2scp6lm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2scp6lm&d=%2Bt1kyFtSusEBwBbR8XkNpwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5539a432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2scp6lm</a>"},{"pid":"dbc6a1ae8fea50506c42dda2e3873d801dfc6634","tid":273401,"uid":140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"泡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0951a0d9c654f2c98fb9483a2080b2072cd8046","tid":273401,"uid":2423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:45:44.000Z","msg":"好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n韓狗死全家"},{"pid":"1271f5bb307c8afe0e78dd6ad16549f4bb6bd5cb","tid":273401,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"人哋冇自殺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鎮定劑喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}